AI BUILD PROMPT: DEAD DROP
A Digital Legacy Platform

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

PROJECT BRIEF

Build a mobile-first application called DEAD DROP that allows users to create 
posthumous content releases. Think: dead man's switch meets meme archive meets 
digital will.

Core concept: Users curate vaults of digital content (memes, messages, media) 
that get released to chosen "executors" after death or extended inactivity.

Brand tone: MSCHF-style â€” brutally honest, darkly humorous, zero corporate speak, 
maximum cultural awareness.

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE

PLATFORM REQUIREMENTS:
- React Native for iOS (priority) and Android
- Node.js/Express backend
- PostgreSQL database
- AWS S3 for media storage
- Redis for session management and trigger monitoring
- End-to-end encryption (AES-256)

CORE SYSTEMS TO BUILD:

1. USER AUTHENTICATION
   - Email/password signup
   - 2FA mandatory for premium users
   - Biometric unlock for app access
   - Session management with auto-logout

2. VAULT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
   - Create/edit/delete vaults
   - Upload multiple content types:
     * Images (JPEG, PNG, GIF, WebP)
     * Videos (MP4, MOV - max 5min for premium)
     * Audio (MP3, M4A - voice memos)
     * Text notes (encrypted)
     * URLs (auto-preview generation)
   - Folder organization within vaults
   - Preview mode (see vault as executor would)
   - Content encryption at rest

3. EXECUTOR SYSTEM
   - Invite executors via email/phone
   - Multi-tier access levels:
     * Primary (full access, can trigger)
     * Curator (specific vaults only)
     * Viewer (read-only access post-release)
   - Executor dashboard showing:
     * User's last activity timestamp
     * Assigned vaults
     * Trigger status
   - Emergency override (requires 3/5 executor vote)

4. TRIGGER MECHANISM
   - Automated inactivity detection:
     * Track app opens, "proof of life" check-ins
     * Configurable thresholds: 90, 180, 365 days
     * Progressive warnings to user (email/push at 60, 75, 85 days)
   - Manual triggers:
     * Death certificate upload + verification
     * Multi-executor confirmation vote
     * Scheduled releases (date-based)
   - 72-hour cancellation window:
     * User can abort trigger from any logged-in device
     * Executors notified of cancellation
   - Notification service for executors

5. MEMORIAL WALL (POST-RELEASE)
   - Public or private vault pages
   - Custom URL slugs (premium)
   - Social features:
     * Emoji reactions
     * Comment threads
     * Upload tribute content
     * Share to social media
   - Content moderation tools
   - Analytics (views, engagement)

6. PROOF OF LIFE SYSTEM
   - Monthly check-in requirement
   - Push notification + email reminders
   - Gamification: streak counter, "still alive" badges
   - Snooze options (vacation mode)
   - Integration with device activity (optional)

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

UI/UX SPECIFICATIONS

DESIGN PRINCIPLES:
- Brutalist minimalism
- High contrast (black/white/red)
- Zero rounded corners on primary UI elements
- Harsh typography (Helvetica Bold, Arial)
- No loading spinners - use text ("LOADING YOUR DEATH...")
- Error states are blunt ("THIS FUCKED UP")

KEY SCREENS TO BUILD:

1. ONBOARDING
   - Dark humor welcome ("Everyone Dies")
   - 3-screen flow:
     * Why this exists
     * How it works
     * Create first vault
   - No skip option on legal disclaimer

2. HOME / DASHBOARD
   - Vault grid (2-column)
   - Prominent "PROOF OF LIFE" button at top
   - Last check-in timestamp
   - Executor count badge
   - Bottom nav: Vaults / Executors / Settings / Profile

3. VAULT CREATION
   - Name vault (text input)
   - Choose icon/emoji
   - Add content (upload/link/text)
   - Set trigger conditions
   - Assign executors
   - Preview button

4. CONTENT UPLOAD
   - Drag and drop (web)
   - Multi-select (mobile)
   - Progress indicators
   - Auto-save drafts
   - Content type icons

5. EXECUTOR MANAGEMENT
   - List view with access levels
   - Invite button (email/SMS)
   - Pending invites status
   - Remove executor (requires confirmation)

6. SETTINGS
   - Account details
   - Security (2FA, biometrics)
   - Notification preferences
   - Subscription management
   - Legal docs (TOS, Privacy)
   - Delete account (nuclear option)

7. MEMORIAL WALL
   - Vault content display (chronological)
   - Reaction bar
   - Comment section
   - Share options
   - "Create Your Own" CTA

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

COPY STYLE GUIDE

VOICE ATTRIBUTES:
- Blunt, never euphemistic
- Self-aware about being morbid
- Zero marketing speak
- Occasional profanity (contextual)
- Deadpan humor

EXAMPLE MICROCOPY:

Buttons:
- "CREATE VAULT" not "Get Started"
- "SEND TO EXECUTORS" not "Share"
- "I'M STILL ALIVE" not "Check In"
- "DELETE FOREVER" not "Remove"

Error Messages:
- "Upload failed. Try again or give up."
- "Password wrong. You have 2 tries left."
- "This vault is empty. Add something or delete it."

Success Messages:
- "Vault created. Plan accordingly."
- "Executor added. They know now."
- "Subscription active. You're premium until death."

Notifications:
- "Haven't seen you in 60 days. Everything ok?"
- "Someone triggered your vault. Check it?"
- "Your proof of life streak: 43 days"

Empty States:
- "No vaults yet. Immortal?"
- "No executors assigned. Trust issues?"
- "No content uploaded. Say something."

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

SUBSCRIPTION TIERS

FREE TIER: "BASIC DEATH"
Features:
- 3 vaults maximum
- 25 total content pieces
- 3 executors
- 6-month inactivity trigger only
- Standard memorial page
- Ads on memorial wall

PREMIUM: "ETERNAL PLAN" ($49/year)
Features:
- Unlimited vaults
- Unlimited content
- Unlimited executors
- Custom trigger timings
- Video uploads (5min max)
- Custom memorial domain
- No ads
- Priority support
- Advanced encryption
- Collaborative vaults

ENTERPRISE: "FAMILY DEATH PACT" ($199/year)
Features:
- 5 linked accounts
- Shared executor network
- Legal document integration
- Dedicated onboarding
- White-glove support
- Custom contracts

PAYMENT:
- Stripe integration
- Annual billing only (no monthly)
- Auto-renewal with warning emails
- Subscription survives user death (executors can access)

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

SECURITY & LEGAL REQUIREMENTS

ENCRYPTION:
- AES-256 for content at rest
- TLS 1.3 for data in transit
- Client-side encryption before upload for "secure vaults"
- Zero-knowledge architecture for premium encrypted vaults

PRIVACY:
- GDPR compliant
- CCPA compliant
- Right to deletion (even after death with executor consent)
- No data selling
- Transparent data usage

CONTENT MODERATION:
- AI-based screening for illegal content
- Report/flag system on memorial walls
- Human review queue
- Content policy enforcement (no hate speech, CSAM, violence)

LEGAL PROTECTIONS:
- Terms of Service including:
  * Liability limitations
  * Content ownership
  * Executor authority boundaries
  * False death claim consequences
  * Dispute resolution
- Privacy Policy
- Acceptable Use Policy
- Death verification process documentation

AGE VERIFICATION:
- 18+ required for account
- Government ID check for premium features

MENTAL HEALTH:
- In-app resources (suicide prevention hotlines)
- Crisis text line integration
- Warning prompts for certain content
- Partnership with mental health orgs

â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”

ANALYTICS & MONITORING

TRACK:
- User engagement:
  * Daily/monthly active users
  * Vaults created per user
  * Content uploaded (by type)
  * Proof of life check-in rate
  * Session length
- Growth metrics:
  * New signups
  * Executor invites sent
  * Viral coefficient
  * Conversion rate (free to premium)
  * Churn rate
- Technical:
  * API response times
  * Error rates
  * Storage usage
  * Trigger success rate
- Financial:
  * MRR/ARR
  * CAC
  * LTV
  * Payment failures

TOOLS:
- Mixpanel or Amplitude for product analytics
- Sentry for error tracking
- CloudWatch for infrastructure
- Custom dashboard for trigger monitoring

