API SPECIFICATIONS

ENDPOINTS TO BUILD:

Authentication:
POST /api/auth/signup
POST /api/auth/login
POST /api/auth/logout
POST /api/auth/refresh
POST /api/auth/verify-2fa

Vaults:
GET /api/vaults
POST /api/vaults
GET /api/vaults/:id
PUT /api/vaults/:id
DELETE /api/vaults/:id
POST /api/vaults/:id/content
DELETE /api/vaults/:id/content/:contentId
GET /api/vaults/:id/preview

Executors:
GET /api/executors
POST /api/executors/invite
DELETE /api/executors/:id
PUT /api/executors/:id/permissions
POST /api/executors/vote-trigger

Triggers:
GET /api/triggers/status
POST /api/triggers/proof-of-life
POST /api/triggers/manual
POST /api/triggers/cancel
GET /api/triggers/history

Memorial:
GET /api/memorial/:vaultId
POST /api/memorial/:vaultId/react
POST /api/memorial/:vaultId/comment
GET /api/memorial/:vaultId/stats

Subscription:
GET /api/subscription
POST /api/subscription/checkout
POST /api/subscription/cancel
GET /api/subscription/invoices

RATE LIMITING:
- Auth endpoints: 5 requests/minute
- Upload endpoints: 20 requests/hour
- API calls: 1000 requests/hour (authenticated)
- Public memorial pages: 100 requests/minute

