SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS

BRAND CONSISTENCY:
- Every UI element should feel slightly uncomfortable
- No hand-holding or "delight" animations
- Copy should always acknowledge the morbid reality
- Errors are honest, never apologetic
- Success feels matter-of-fact

PERFORMANCE:
- <2s page load times
- <100ms API responses
- Aggressive caching for memorial pages
- CDN for media content
- Lazy loading for vault grids

ACCESSIBILITY:
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Screen reader optimization
- Keyboard navigation
- High contrast mode
- Closed captions on videos

TESTING:
- Unit tests for critical paths
- Integration tests for triggers
- End-to-end tests for core flows
- Load testing for memorial walls
- Security penetration testing

DOCUMENTATION:
- API documentation (OpenAPI spec)
- Developer onboarding guide
- Architecture decision records
- Runbook for production incidents
- User guide (minimal, sardonic)

