BUILD PRIORITIES

SPRINT 1 (Weeks 1-2):
- Auth system
- Database schema
- Vault CRUD operations
- Basic UI framework

SPRINT 2 (Weeks 3-4):
- Content upload system
- Executor invites
- Proof of life mechanism
- Trigger infrastructure

SPRINT 3 (Weeks 5-6):
- Memorial wall
- Subscription integration
- Email notifications
- Security hardening

SPRINT 4 (Weeks 7-8):
- Polish UI
- Performance optimization
- Testing
- Beta launch prep

